    "---\n",
    "layout: post\n",
    "title: Outfit Picker\n",
    "description: Don't know what to wear to school every day? Don't have the time or care to create an outfit? Don't worry, add your clothes to the closet and generate an outfit depending on the temperature.\n",
    "type: ccc\n",
    "comments: False\n",
    "permalink: /clothes/outfitpicker\n",
    "menu: nav/clothes.html\n",
    "---"
   ]
